skdetail:

Invocation Name: what day is it
des:
Use this skill to hear the date, what day of the year it is, and how many days are left in the year.

Open the skill each day to remain fully aware of what day it is!

To use, simply say, "Alexa open what day is it!"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
